\id HEB - draft by Siria and Arnold and Steven Oct 2000; exeg ck by Marsha and Steven and Gabby May 2001; comprehension ck June 2002 by John Relyea and a large group; consultant ck Jan 03 with Mike Sweeney and a group; revisions by Francis and Marsha Aug 03; ready for publication. Published with 2004 Aruamu NT. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus. 
\h Hibru 
\toc3 HI 
\toc2 Hibru 
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Hibrun Gumazamiziba Bagha Zuim 
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Hibrun Gumazamiziba Bagha Zuim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Hibru 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Judabar marazi faragha uan navibagh iragha Krais…®n g…®n zui, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim atagh…®raghasava ami. Kamagh…®n, ak…®nafarir kam gumazir mam o amizir mam me bagha an osiri. E fozir pu, tinaram an osiri, ak…®nafarim…®n aven gumazim o amizim uan ziam d…®borozir puvat…®. Marazi ghaze, Pol, o Barnabas, o Apolos, o Prisila, men tav ti an osiri. 
\ip Gumazir maba Krais…®n g…®n zuir gumazamiziba d…®kab…®ra egha os…®mt…®ziba me gan…®di. Ak…®nafarir kam men n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba gavgavim dar an…®ngasa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ingangarir ekiar God Krais Iesus…®n aven amizim, gun me m…®gei. Kraisra guizbang…®n God…®n arazim en akakasi. 
\ip Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam bizir ekiar pumuning ko m…®kezim m…®gei. 1. Iesus a guizbang…®ra God…®n Otarim. Dughiar Iesus nguazim…®n itim, an os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ko m…®zaziba ini. Ez…® arazir kam…®n God Iesus gamiz…®, a gumazamizibar akurvaghamin faragha zuir gumazim…®n oto. (2:10) Egha Iesus akam inigha izir gumazir fom…®ra itiba ko enselba ko Moses gafira. 2. God uab…® Iesus am…®sevez…® a ofa gamir gumazim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam, egha a Judabar ofa gamir gumazibagh afira. 3. Iesus a God…®n Nguibam…®n Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n iti. Egh gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, a ua me iniam. Moses Osirizir Araziba, God bagha ofa gamir arazibar gun m…®gei, da pura Iesus amizir ingangarir ekiar kam…®n nedaziba. 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim, gavgavim dar an…®ngasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Israelian gumazamizir fom…®ra itibar n…®ghn…®zir bar gavgavim…®n akaba iti (sapta 11). A ghaze, mark…®, os…®mt…®zir manam me bato, me uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n suiraghv…®ra ik…® mang…®va ovengegh. Me Iesus…®n gan an arazibar g…®n mang…®, egh os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zazir me isiba batogh. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Iesus, a enselbagh afira 
\mr (Sapta 1--2) 
\s1 God e m…®k…®masa uan akam isa uan Otarim gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 1 Fom…®ra God dughiar av…®riba ko tuavir av…®ribar uan akam isa an akam inigha izir gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®, me en inazir afeziabav keme.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Onger Akaba 2:8; Jon 1:3; Efesus 1:10\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam, kar dughiar abuananaba, God e m…®k…®masa uan akam isa uan Otarim gan…®ngi. God biziba bar da iniasava Otarir kam am…®sefe. Otarir kam…®n agharim…®n, God fom…®ra overiam ko nguazim…®n ingari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Aposel 2:33-34; 2 Korin 4:4; Kolosi 1:15-17; 1:20; Hibru 8:1; Akar Mogomem 4:11\x*Ez…® Otarir kamra God…®n angazangarim en akagha ghaze, God a bar dera. Egha uaghan a God…®n m…®rara gari. An akam bar gavgafi, egha akar kamra a bar bizibagh amima, da gavgavighav…®ra iti. Egha an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ingangarim ag…®vagha, gumazamizibagh amima me zuegha iti. Egha a g…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabogha P…®n Tir Atrivir Ekiam…®n agharir guvim…®n borogh…®n apera. 
\s1 God…®n Otarim enselbagh afira 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Efesus 1:21; Filipai 2:9-10\x*Afeziam ziam uan Otarim gan…®ngi. Ez…® ziar kam a bar dera, egha enselbar ziabagh afira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an Otarim gamiz…®ma a enselbar ekiam…®n oto, ez…® me an apengan iti.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 2 Samuel 7:14; 1 Eghaghaniba 17:13; Onger Akaba 2:7; 89:26-27; Aposel 13:33; Hibru 5:5\x*Egha God dughiatam uan ensel…®n tam kamagh…®n a m…®kemezir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…®n Afeziam…®n oto.‚Äù O a kamagh…®n ensel…®n tam m…®kemezir puvat…®, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® ia inigh, egh ian Afeziam…®n m…®n ik…®t…®, ia nan Otarim…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù Bar puvat…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:43; Rom 8:29; Kolosi 1:18; 1 Pita 3:22; Akar Mogomem 1:5\x*Egha dughiar God ua uan Otarir ivariam nguazir kam…®n anemangasa uaghan ghaze: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGod…®n enselba bar an apengan ik…®va 
\q2 an ziam fam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Onger Akaba 104:4\x*God enselbagh n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA uan enselbagh amima da am…®nim…®n m…®n otifi, egha uan ingangarir gumazibagh amima me avir m…®zariabar m…®n otifi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8-9 \xt Onger Akaba 45:6-7\x*Egha Otarim g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…®n atrivir dabirabir God n…® gan…®ngizim, 
\q2 a zurara ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Eght…® n…® guiz…®n arazim…®n 
\q2 uan gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam. 
\q1  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Aisaia 61:1; Aposel 4:27; 10:38\x*N…® arazir aghuibara ifuegha, egha arazir kuraba bar dar aghua. 
\q1 Kamagh amiz…®, God n…® am…®sevegha, 
\q2 n…® ziar ekiam ikiasa 
\q3 a borem n…®n dapanim ginge. 
\q1 A kamagh…®n n…® gamiz…® 
\q2 n…® bar akonge, 
\q1 ez…® n…® bar akongezir bizir kam, 
\q2 atrivir igharaziba bar me gafira.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10-12 \xt Onger Akaba 102:25-27\x*Egha God uan Otarim kamagh…®n a m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ingari. 
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, n…® uab…® uan dafaribar overiam ko bizir p…®n itibar ingari. 
\q1  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Aisaia 34:4; 2 Pita 3:7; 3:10\x*Bizir kaba bar g…®vagham, 
\q2 eght…® n…® ik…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\q1 Overiam ko nguazim, aning bar ikuvigham, 
\q2 mati inim ghurigha bar b…®aghire. 
\q1  
\v 12 N…® aning righam, 
\q2 mati gumazim atuim r…®ki. 
\q1 N…® aning damight…® aning igharagh otogham, 
\q2 mati gumazim korotiar ghuriba suaghar…®si. 
\q1 Ez…® n…®, kamagh…®ra iti, n…® igharagha garir puvat…®. 
\q2 N…®n dughiam g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Onger Akaba 110:1; Matyu 22:44; Mak 12:36; Luk 20:42\x*Fom…®ra God kamagh…®n uan Otarimra kamagh…®n a m…®keme, ‚ÄúN…® nan agharir guvim…®n daperagh ik…® mang…®t…®, k…® n…®n apaniba d…®kab…®ragh me is…® n…®n dafarim dat…®ght…® me n…®n dagarimning…®n apengan ikiam.‚Äù Egha God dughiatam…®n akar katam ensel…®n tam m…®kemezir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Onger Akaba 34:7; 91:11; Matyu 18:10; Aposel 12:7; Jems 2:5\x*Guizbang…®ra enselba me duaba, egha me God…®n ingangarim gami. Ez…® God gumazamizir a ua iniamibar akurvaghasa me amadi, me arui. 
\c 2  
\s1 God en akurazir arazim,  // a bizir bar ekiam 
\p  
\v 1 God…®n Otarim ziar ekiam isi, kamagh…®n amiz…®, akar e oraghizir kamnagh, e bar m…®ghv…®ram an suiragham. E ireghan koghs…®, e akar kam deraghv…®ra an suiragh gavgavigh ikiam.  
\v 2 Fom…®ra God en inazir afeziabav k…®masa, uan akam isa enselbagh an…®ngi, egha kamagh…®ra tuavir kam…®n a kamagh…®n men aka, akar kam a guizbang…®ra. Ez…® gumazamiziba akar kam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®gha a batoke, me ivezir kuram iniam. Men arazir kurar me amizibar m…®rara, me uan ivezir kuram inis.\f + \fr 2:2 \ft Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir God Moses gan…®ngizim m…®gei. N…® Ua Me Ini 19-20…®n gan. Ua Me Iniamin Ak…®nafarim…®n akam, ensel…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba puvat…®, ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, God Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim enselbar dafarim…®n Moses gan…®ngi. Ia Aposel 7:38 ko 7:53, ko Galesia 3:19…®n gan.\f* 
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Matyu 4:17; Mak 1:14; Luk 1:2; Hibru 10:28-29; 12:25\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, God en akurazir arazim, a bizir bar ekiam. E ak…®rim ragh God…®n akurvazir arazim gasaragh…®va, e manmagh…®n arazir kuram…®n ivezim gitagham. Bar puvat…®gham. Ekiam uab…® faragha en akurvaghasa m…®keme, ez…® gumazamiziba an akam baraki. Ez…® me kamagh…®n m…®g…®a en aka, akar kamnagh a guizbang…®ra.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mak 16:20; Aposel 2:22; 14:3; 1 Korin 2:4; 12:4; 12:7; 12:11; Efesus 1:5; 1:9\x*Dughiar kam…®n, God mirakel…®n igharagha gariba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibagh amua uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua God…®n Duam…®n bizir aghuiba tuiragha gumazamizibagh an…®di. Ez…® arazir kam…®n a kamagh…®n en aka, an Otarim…®n akar kam a bar guizbang…®ra ghu. 
\s1 Iesus, a uab…® en Akurvazir Gumazim 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Hibru 6:5; 2 Pita 3:13\x*E nguazir igiar God g…®n damight…® otivamim g…®n…®ghn…®gh fogham, God nguazir igiar kam gativasa, enselbav kemezir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jop 7:17; Onger Akaba 144:3\x*\x - \xo 2:6-8 \xt Onger Akaba 8:4-6\x*Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven akar mam kamagh…®n iti: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúO God! E gumazamiziba ti manmagh…®ram amizir biziba, ez…® n…® m…®gh…®gha e g…®n…®ghn…®si? 
\q2 E pura biziba. Manmagh…®ram amiz…®, n…® bar puv…®ram e g…®n…®ghn…®si? 
\q1  
\v 7 N…® uab…® en ingarigha, e isa enselbar apengan e at…®. 
\q2 N…® gavgavim ko ziar ekiam isa e gan…®ga e afaz…®, bizir n…® ingariziba bar en apengan iti. 
\q1  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Matyu 28:18; 1 Korin 15:25-27; Efesus 1:22\x*Biziba bar mogh…®ra n…® da isa e gumazamiziba en suemning…®n apengan da ar…®ki. 
\q2 Eght…® e bar dagh ativagham.‚Äù 
\b  
\m God…®n akar kam ghaze, God gumazamizibagh amiz…®, biziba bar men apengan ik…®t…® me dagh ativagham. Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim a kamak…®n, God bizir a ingariziba bar da isa en apengan da ar…®ki. Ez…® e fo, dat…®r…®gh…®n e garima, biziba bar en apengan itir puvat…®.\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Akar Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itim, a gumazamiziba bar me m…®gei. Ez…® gumazir Hibrun Ak…®nafarim…®n Osirizim, a Iesus g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, a gumazim…®n m…®n otogha gumazamiziba bar men danganim ini. Ez…® kamagh…®n Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim…®n, a bizir guiz…®n Iesus batozibav gei.\f* 
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Jon 3:16; Rom 5:18; Filipai 2:7-9; 1 Timoti 2:6; 1 Jon 2:2; Akar Mogomem 5:9\x*Ez…® e Iesus g…®fo, a ziar ekiam ini. God kamaghsua, a bar en apangkuvight…®, tuavir kam…®n Iesus gumazamiziba bagh aremegham. Egha kamagh…®n bar dughiar otevim…®n an enselbar apengan ike. Egha m…®zazir dafam inigha areme, ez…® bizir kam bagha God ziar ekiam a gan…®ga a ghufe.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Luk 24:46; Aposel 3:15; Rom 8:29; 11:36; Hibru 5:9; 10:10\x*E fo, God a biziba bar dar m…®ngarim, egha a biziba bar dar ingari. Egha kamagh…®n ifonge, Iesus uan borir av…®riba inigh men aku God…®n Nguibam…®n mangam, eght…® me Iesus ko ziar ekiam iniam. God kamagh…®n ifonge, Iesus gumazamizibar akurvaghamin ingangarim damuam, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Iesus ataghiz…®ma a m…®zazim isi. Ez…® m…®zazir kam Iesus gamima a gumazamizibar akurvaghamin gumazir bar faragha zuim…®n otogha, tuavim men aka. Arazir God a gamir kam, a bar dera. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Matyu 25:40; Mak 3:35; Jon 20:17; Aposel 17:26; Rom 8:29\x*E fo, gumazir kam Iesus, a gumazamizibagh amiz…® me God…®n gumazamizibar m…®n ikia egha me bar zue. A me ko afeziar vam…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an aghums…®zir puvat…®gha me d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúNan aveghbuaba ko buaramiziba.‚Äù  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Onger Akaba 22:22\x*Egha a kamagh…®n God m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® uan adarazir tong…®n ik…® 
\q2 n…®n ziam…®n gun me m…®k…®mam. 
\q1 K…® gumazamiziba uari akuvamin danganim…®n ik…® 
\q2 men tong…®n n…®n ziam fam.‚Äù 
\b  
\m  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Onger Akaba 18:2; Jon 17:6; 17:9-12\x*Egha a ua ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, God damuasa m…®kemezir biziba, k…® puram a m…®zuam da bagh gan ik…®t…® God damuasa amir biziba, a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n dar amuam.‚Äù Egha ua ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gan, k…® borir God na gan…®ngiziba me ko iti.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:13 \ft Iesus…®n akar kam, a Aisaia 8:17-18…®n ize. Gumazim o amizir Hibrun Ak…®nafarim Osirizim, en akaght…® e fogham, Iesus gumazamizir igharaziba ko magh gari, me an aveghbuaba ko an boriba. Ez…® gumazamiziba God m…®zuaima a bizibagh ami, ez…® Iesus uaghan orarti.\f* 
\s1 Iesus en akuraghasa gumazim…®n m…®n oto 
\p  
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 2:14-15 \xt Jon 1:14; 12:31; Rom 8:3; 8:15; Filipai 2:7; Kolosi 2:15; 2 Timoti 1:7; 1 Jon 3:8; Akar Mogomem 12:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, borir kaba, me guizbang…®ra inivaf…®ziba ko ghuziba iti. Kamagh…®ra Iesus uaghan men m…®n ikia guiz…®n gumazim…®n oto. A kamaghsua, an aremegh egh arazir kam…®n a Satan bar a gas…®ghasigham, a gumazir gumazamizibagh amima me ariaghirir gavgavim itim. Gumazamiziba nguazir kam…®n ikiava ovevem…®n atiati. Ez…® men atiatir kam me ikiaghar…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Iesus me f…®rasa, bizir kam bagha, a gumazim…®n m…®n otogha egha areme.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Aisaia 41:8-9\x*Guizbang…®ra, Iesus ingangarir kam enselbar akurvaghasa a gamizir pu. Puvat…®. An Abraham…®n boriba akurvaghasa a gami.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Filipai 2:7; Hibru 2:14; 4:15; 5:1-2; 1 Jon 2:2; 4:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan doziba ko buaramizibar m…®raram oto. A kamaghsua, a men Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n ik…®, egh God…®n akam…®n g…®n mang…® apangkuvim gumazamizibar ik…®va God…®n ingangarim damu, egh ingangarir kam…®n gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amangam. Kamagh…®n a gumazamizibar m…®n oto.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Hibru 4:15-16; 5:2; 7:25\x*Ez…® Satan a gifarasa arazir kuraba bagha a gakaghori, ez…® an os…®mt…®ziba ateri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Satan gumazamizibagh ifaramin dughiabar, Iesus men akurvaghamin fofozim iti. 
\c 3  
\ms1 Iesus…®n ziar ekiam, a bar Moses…®n ziar ekiam gafira 
\mr (Sapta 3:1--4:13) 
\s1 Iesus…®n ziar ekiam, a Moses…®n ziar ekiam gafira 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Efesus 4:1; Filipai 3:14; Hibru 4:14; 5:5; 6:20; 7:26; 8:1; 9:11; 2 Pita 1:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Krais…®n adarasi, God uaghan Uan Nguibam…®n mangasa, a ian dia. Ia derav…®ra Iesus g…®n…®ghn…®gh, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia, egha an ziam…®n gun m…®g…®a ghaze, a God m…®sevegha amadazir abuir gumazim, egha uaghan Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt D…®boboniba 12:7\x*God anem…®sevegha ingangarir kam a gan…®ngiz…®, a God…®n gumazamiziba bagha ingari. Moses fom…®ra God…®n gumazamiziba bagha derav…®ra ingariz…® mogh…®ra, a ingari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Sekaraia 6:12; Matyu 16:18\x*E fo, gumazir d…®penim…®n ingarim, a ziar ekiam isi, ez…® an ziar ekiam, an d…®penim…®n ziar ekiam gafira. Ez…® kamagh…®ra God ziar ekiam Iesus gan…®ngi, ez…® an ziar ekiam, Moses…®n ziar ekiam gafira.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Efesus 2:10; 3:9; Hibru 1:2\x*Ez…® d…®peniba bar, gumaziba dar ingari. Ez…® Godra, a biziba bar dar ingari.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt D…®boboniba 12:7\x*Moses a God…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n iti, egha God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua God…®n gumazamiziba bagha derav…®ra ingari. A bizibar gun m…®k…®mamin ingangarim iti, akar God g…®n a m…®k…®mamiba.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Rom 5:2; Efesus 2:21-22; Kolosi 1:23; 1 Timoti 3:15; Hibru 3:14; 6:11; 1 Pita 2:5\x*Ez…® Krais a God…®n Otarim, a God…®n gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam. Egha guizbang…®ra God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua ingangarir kam derav…®ra a gami. Eght…® e atiatingan kogh…®va, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va egh bizir aghuir e iniamiba e dav zuamam, egh kamagh…®n damuva, e uaghan God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®n ikiam. 
\s1 Gumazir akaba batoziba, me aghuvsazim inian kogham 
\p  
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 3:7-11 \xt Onger Akaba 95:7-11\x*\x - \xo 3:7-8 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:7; D…®boboniba 20:2-5\x*E God…®n gumazamiziba, egha uaghan an d…®penim…®n m…®n iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, e God…®n Duam…®n akam baragham. A kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIa dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n tiarim baragh…®va, 
\q2 egh ia uan navibar kuman mark…®, 
\q3 mati ian inazir afeziaba fom…®ra an akaba batogha 
\q4 orazir puvat…®. 
\q1 Me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia God damut…® a irasa an akam batosi. 
\q1  
\v 9 God ghaze, 
\q2 Me danganir kam…®n ikia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itir puvat…®gha, 
\q3 nan gavgavim tuis…®gh fofoghasa nan azai. 
\q1 Me garima, 
\q2 k…® 40plan azenibar arazir aghuiba me bagha dagh ami. 
\q1  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bar gumazamizir kabar an…®ngaghegha ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòGumazamizir kabar naviba bar saghon ikia nan g…®n zuir puvat…®. 
\q3 Me zurara tuavir k…® me bagh at…®zim gitav…®rasi.‚Äô 
\q1  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt D…®boboniba 14:21-23\x*K…® men an…®ngaghegha bar guizbang…®ra akar gavgavim gamua ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòMe nan aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham. 
\q3 Bar puvat…®!‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 12 Krais…®n adarasi, ia uari bagh derav…®ra gan, ian tong…®n tav n…®ghn…®zir kuratam an navir averiam…®n ik…®t…® a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ategh, ak…®rim ragh Angam…®ra Itir God gasan mark…®.  
\v 13 Ez…® ia kamagh…®n damuan mark…®, ia kamagh…®n damu, ia zurara dughiabar ia vaghvagh God…®n gumazamizir igharaziba ko ia, akar aghuim uari dan…®ng uarir akurvagh egh uan naviba gavgavim dar an…®ng. Kamagh…®n arazir kuram tav gifaraght…®, a God…®n g…®n zuir tuavim ateghan kogham. God…®n Ak…®nafarim ghaze, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù e fo, e dat…®r…®gh…®n ingangarir kam damuam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Hibru 3:6\x*Ia fo, dughiar e faragha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itim, en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar gavgafi. Egh e uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar amut…® da gavgavigh ik…® magh…®ra mang…® dughiar e ovengamim…®n otogham. E kamagh…®n damuva, e bar Krais ko porogh…®v ik…® a ko ingar ikiam.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Onger Akaba 95:7-8; Hibru 3:7-8\x*E fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n ia God…®n tiarim baragh…®va, 
\q2 egh ia an akam…®n aghuaghan mark…®, 
\q1 mati ian inazir afeziaba fom…®ra an akaba batogha 
\q2 egha orazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:25-38\x*\x - \xo 3:16-18 \xt D…®boboniba 14:1-35\x*Fom…®ra te God…®n tiarim baregha, an g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha an akam batosi? Kar gumazamizir Moses inigha Isip…®n ghueziba, meraram arazir kam gami.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Onger Akaba 106:26; 1 Korin 10:10; Jut 1:5\x*Ez…® God 40plan azenibar ten an…®ngaghe? A gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiziba, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ariaghirezir gumaziba, merara, a men an…®ngaghe.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:34-35; Hibru 3:11\x*God fom…®ra guizbang…®ra akar gavgavim ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúMe nan aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mangan kogham.‚Äù Akar kam, a te gan…®ngi? Kar gumazamizir an akam barazir puvat…®ziba. A me baghv…®ra m…®gei.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Hibru 4:6\x*Kamagh…®n e fo, gumazir kaba me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikian aghua. Ez…® bizir kam bagha me God…®n aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mangan ibura. 
\c 4  
\s1 God…®n gumazamiziba aghuvsazim iniam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Hibru 12:15\x*Dat…®r…®gh…®n, God uaghan e inigh aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mangasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® kamagh…®n ia uari bagh derav…®ra gan, ian tav atam akuigh egh danganir kam…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham.  
\v 2 E Akar Aghuim baraki, mati fom…®ra Israelia a baraki. Egha Israelia me puram akam a baraki, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®. Ez…® bizir kam bagha Akar Aghuir me oraghizir kam, a men akurazir puvat…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Onger Akaba 95:11; Hibru 3:11\x*Ez…® e gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itiba, an e ateght…®ma e an aghuvsazir danganim…®n mangam. A fom…®ra nguibar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha egha a m…®kemezir mogh…®ra: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® an…®ngaghegha akar gavgavim ak…®ra ghaze, 
\q2 ‚ÄòMe nan aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham. 
\q3 Bar puvat…®!‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\m Guizbang…®ra, God Moses…®n dughiam…®n akar kam m…®gei, ez…® e fo, bar fom…®ra dughiar a nguazir kam…®n ingarizim, a nguazir kam…®n ingarasa n…®ghn…®ziba a dagh amigha g…®fa.\f + \fr 4:3 \ft Israelia Isip ataghizir dughiam, God Moses ko Josua me inigh Kenan…®n Nguazim…®n mangasa a ifonge, eght…® nguazir kam me dapiagh avughsamin danganim…®n otogham. Ez…® gumazir Hibrun Ak…®nafarim osirizim kamagh…®n en aka, God avughs…®zir danganir igharazim iti, kar God…®n Nguibam, guizbang…®ram an avughsazir danganim, eght…® gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itibarama Nguibar kam…®n aven mangan.\f* 
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Jenesis 2:2; Ua Me Ini 20:11; 31:17\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven akar otevir mam iti, a namba 7…®n dughiam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAruer namba 7…®n, God garima an ingangariba bar g…®fa, ez…® a dughiar kam…®n avughse.‚Äù  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Onger Akaba 95:11\x*Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kamra e faragha a baraki, a ua m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe nan aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®!‚Äù  
\v 6 E kamagh…®n bizir kam g…®fo, God…®n aghuvsazir danganir kam a ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® gumazamizitaba an aven mangam. Ez…® gumazamizir faragha Akar Aghuim baraghiziba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me aven ghuezir puvat…®.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Onger Akaba 95:7-8\x*Ez…® gumazamizir kabar g…®n, azenir av…®riba ghua g…®fa, ez…® God uan akam isa Devit gan…®ngi, k…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir akar kam…®n gun m…®kemegha g…®fa. A ghaze: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n ia God…®n tiarim baragh…®va, 
\q2 egh ia an akam…®n aghuaghan mark…®.‚Äù 
\b  
\m Devit…®n dughiam…®n, God ghaze, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù egha kamagh…®n en aka, a dughiar igharazim ginaba. Dughiar a inabazir kam, gumazamiziba an aghuvsazir danganir kam…®n aven mangam.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:7; Josua 22:4\x*Josua ti fom…®ra aghuvsazim gumazamizibagh an…®ngiz…®, ez…® God g…®n dughiar igharazitam ginabaghan koghai.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e fo, God…®n gumazamizibar aghuvsazim a ik…®v…®ra ikiam, a mati Sabat…®n aghuvsazir dughiam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Jenesis 2:2; Hibru 4:4\x*E fo, gumazim God…®n aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven ghua, a uan ingangarim ag…®vagha aghuvsi, mati fom…®ra God uan ingangarim ag…®vaghava aghuvsi. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Hibru 3:12; 3:18-19\x*E kamagh…®n aghua, me fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, gumazitam o amizitam uan akaba batozir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®, aremegh uan aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n e aghuvsazir danganim…®n aven mang…®s…® pamtem…®n ingaram. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Aisaia 49:2; Jeremaia 23:29; Jon 12:48; Efesus 6:17; Akar Mogomem 1:16; 19:15\x*God…®n Akam an angam…®ra ikia, egha pamtem…®n ingara iti. A bar ghumigha, m…®dorozir sabar ghumt…®zir pumuning itim gafira. Ez…® akar kam, sabar ghumt…®zim…®n m…®n, a bar gumazim…®n namnam okoregha bar aven ghua, duam ko navir averiam uaning bativi nagh…®n oto, egha uaghan aghariba uari isasuirazir nagh…®n, ko agharibar aven itir ovim, aning uaning bativi nagh…®n oto. Egha a bar en n…®ghn…®ziba ko en navir averiabar aven itir ifongiabagh fogha da tuis…®si.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Jop 26:6; Onger Akaba 33:13-14; 90:8; Aghuzir Akaba 15:11\x*Ez…® bizir God ingariziba, tam God…®n damazim…®n modoghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. Ez…® biziba bar kuiaghiregha God…®n damazim…®n bar azenara ikiam. Eght…® Godra arazir e amiba tuis…®ght…®ma e dar a geghanam. 
\ms1 Iesus God…®n Nguibam…®n ikia, en Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n m…®n ikia, egha Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam…®n abuir gumazim…®n m…®n iti 
\mr (Sapta 4:14--10:39) 
\s1 Iesus Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Hibru 3:1; 7:26; 10:23\x*Ez…® e Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanir mam iti, ez…® a bar God…®n Nguibam…®n aven ghu. A Iesus, God…®n Otarim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir e gun m…®geir kam…®n suiragh gavgavigham.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt 2 Korin 5:21; Hibru 2:17; 7:26; 1 Pita 2:22; 1 Jon 3:5\x*E uari arazir kuraba d…®kab…®namin gavgaviba puvat…®. Egh e kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanir kam, en n…®ghn…®zibagh fogh en kuarkuvighan kogham. Puvat…®. Satan…®n ifavarir arazir e bativiziba, da uaghan bar a bativigha g…®fa. Ez…® an arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Efesus 2:18; 3:12; Hibru 10:19-22\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, e atiatingan kogh…®va God…®n atrivir dabirabim…®n borogh…®n mangam, God…®n apangkuvim a giz…®fa. E a bagh mang…®t…®ma God en kuarkuvigh en apangkuvigham. Egh e os…®mt…®zitam ik…®t…® an apangkuvim en akuragham. 
\c 5  
\s1 Iesus, en Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim, an en akura 
\p  
\v 1 Ia n…®ghn…®gh. Ofa gamir gumazibar dapaniba bar, God vaghvagha men adarazir tong…®n me am…®sefe. God men mav am…®sevez…®ma, a gumazamiziba bagha God…®n ofa gami. Egha uaghan bizir aghuiba isa God gan…®di. Egha arazir kuraba bagha ofa gamima God arazir kuraba g…®n amadi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Hibru 2:18; 4:15\x*Egha a uab…® a God…®n damazim…®n bizibar amuamin gavgaviba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir fofoziba puvat…®gha pazav amiba, a men asughasusi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt Ofa Gami 9:7; 16:6; Hibru 7:27\x*Egha a uab…® a bizibar amuamin gavgaviba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ko a uan arazir kuraba sara g…®n amang…®s…® ofabar amu. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Ua Me Ini 28:1\x*Ez…® gumazitam ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n ikiasa uab…® uab…® am…®sevegha ziar ekiam inizir pu. Puvat…®. God uab…® an diaz…®ma a ingangarir kam ini. Mati God fom…®ra Aron…®n diaz…® mok…®n.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Onger Akaba 2:7; Jon 8:54; Hibru 1:5; 1:8\x*Ez…® kamagh…®n, Krais uaghan kamagh…®ram ami. A uab…® uan ziam fer puvat…®, egha Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n otozir pu. Puvat…®, God uab…® ingangarir kam damuasa anem…®sefe. Egha God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® n…®n Afeziam…®n oto.‚Äù  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Onger Akaba 110:4; Hibru 6:20; 7:1; 7:17; 7:21\x*Egha uan Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir akar igharazir mam, a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ofa gamir gumazim, Melkisedek…®n m…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Jon 12:27; 17:1\x*Ez…® dughiar Iesus nguazim…®n itim, a pamtem…®n God ko m…®g…®a egha diav azi. A fo, an ovengan koghs…®, God an akuraghamin gavgavim iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…® uan ifongiam d…®kab…®ragha God…®n apengan ikia, an akam barasi. Ez…® God an d…®mdiam barasi.\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Iesus Getsemanin Azenim…®n ikia, egha os…®mt…®zir a bativamim batoghasa God ko m…®gei. N…® Matyu 26:36-46 ko Mak 14:32-42 ko Luk 22:39-46…®n gan. M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabar God Iesus a ko m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraki. Guizbang…®ra God Iesus ataghiz…® an areme, egha God ovevem ataghiz…® an an suirazir puvat…®. God a gamiz…® ua mozim…®n d…®kaviz…®, a ziar ekiam a ganigha a gamiz…® an Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n oto. N…® uaghan Aposel 2:24 ko Hibru 2:29 ko Filipai 2:6-11…®n gan.\f* 
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Filipai 2:8; Hibru 3:6\x*Guizbang…®ra Iesus a God…®n Otarim, egha a m…®zazim ini. Ez…® tuavir kamra a God…®n akam…®n g…®n zuir arazim an a g…®fo.  
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 5:9-10 \xt Hibru 2:10; 5:6; 11:40\x*Egha a uan ingangarir a damuamiba, a bar da g…®fa. Ez…® God anem…®sevegha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n ikiam, egh Melkisedek…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù Ez…® a gumazamizir an akam baragha an g…®n zuiba, a men Akurvazir Gumazim…®n oto. Egh a men akurvaght…® me derav…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\s1 E borir agh…®ribar m…®n ikian kogham 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Matyu 13:15; Jon 16:12; 2 Pita 3:16\x*E fo, Iesus Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n oto, ez…® e m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®riba akar kam…®n iti, e dar gun ia m…®k…®masa. Ez…® ia oraghan aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, e akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ia m…®k…®man ibura.\f + \fr 5:11 \ft N…® Hibru sapta 7…®n gan.\f* 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt 1 Korin 3:1-3; Hibru 6:1\x*\x - \xo 5:12-13 \xt 1 Korin 3:2\x*Ia fom…®ra Krais…®n adarazir otivigha g…®fa, ez…® kamagh…®n ia gumazamizibar God…®n akam men sure gamighai. Puvat…®, ian n…®ghn…®ziba oteveghav…®ra iti, kamagh…®n gumazir igharaziba, God…®n akar faraghav…®ra ian sure gamiziba, me ua ian sure damuam. Ia dagher gavgaviba inian f…®r…®n, ia otem apav…®ra iti.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt 1 Korin 13:11; Efesus 4:14; 1 Pita 2:2\x*Ez…® tina otem apav…®ra iti, an agh…®rimra iti. Egha an arazir aghuim…®n akar m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Aisaia 7:15; Rom 16:19; 1 Korin 2:14-15; Filipai 1:10\x*Ez…® dagher gavgaviba, da gumazir aruabar daghem. Ez…® gumazir kaba, me dughiar av…®ribar araziba tuis…®si, arazir manam dera ez…® arazir manam ikufi. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me derav…®ra fofoghava egha me n…®ghn…®zir d…®k…®riaba iti. 
\c 6  
\s1 E deraghv…®ra tuivigh gavgavigh God m…®zuamt…®, a derav…®ram e damuam 
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 6:1-2 \xt Aposel 8:14-17; 17:31-32; 19:4-5; Rom 2:16; Filipai 3:12-14; Hibru 5:12; 9:14\x*E dat…®r…®gh…®n Krais…®n adarazir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar faragha iniziba atagh…®ragham, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba: navibagh ighegh ak…®rim ragh ovever arazibagh asaraghamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikiamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, rurir arazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, dafariba gumazibagh is…®n ar…®zir arazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, gumazamizir ovegha ua d…®kavibar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, God gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®ght…® me m…®zaziba iniam, o zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, e m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba ateght…®, da zurara en n…®ghn…®zibar ikian kogham. E kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ik…®va, mati e d…®penir ak…®niba dughiar av…®ribar da akurav…®ra iti, egh d…®penim asaraghan kogham. E gumazir aruabar m…®n akaba baragh egh dar g…®n mangam.\f + \fr 6:1-2 \ft Rurir guar av…®ribagh isir arazim…®n akar kam, a Grigh…®n akam…®n deragha otozir puvat…®. Gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, akar kam Krais…®n adarazir rurim m…®geir puvat…®. A Judabar arazir me g…®n ghua rua God…®n damazim…®n zuer akam m…®gei.\f* 
\v 3 God en amamangat…®ght…®ma, e kamagh…®n damuam. 
\p  
\v 4-6 \x - \xo 6:4-6 \xt Matyu 12:31; Galesia 3:2; Efesus 2:8; Hibru 10:26-27; 10:29; 10:32; 1 Pita 2:3; 2 Pita 2:20-21; 1 Jon 5:16\x*Gumazir maba, God…®n angazangarim…®n aven ikegha, akurvazir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n izezim inigha ghaze, a bar dera, egha igharaz darazi ko, God…®n Duam inis. Egha God…®n akam baregha fo, a bar dera. Me God…®n gavgavim…®n aven ghua deragha an gani, gavgavir kam, a g…®n izamim dughiam…®n m…®sevegh…®r…®gh azenim…®n otogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazim ak…®rim ragh God gasaragh tuavir manatam…®n iz…® ua navim giragham? Bar puvat…®. A kamagh…®n amua, mati, a uan navir averiam…®n aven God…®n Otarim uam a isa ter ighuvim gafugha, a guraz…® gumaziba ua d…®bovir akabar a m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba ataghizir kaba, me ua navibagh iraghamin tuaviba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 7 Amozim dughiar av…®ribar izava nguazim…®n aven zui. Eght…® nguazim daghebar amut…® dagher aghuiba otivam, egh gumazir me me bagha da oparizibar akurvagham. Eght…® God nguazir kam deragh a damuam.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Jenesis 3:17-18\x*Eght…® benir ataghatariba ko benir kuraba an ik…®t…®, kamagh…®n nguazim ikuvigham. A dughiar ruarim ikeghan kogham, eght…® God suam, n…® ikufi, n…® bar isigham. 
\p  
\v 9 Namakar aghuiba, e m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavir kabar ia gami. Egha e ia g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n fo, ia tuavir aghuim…®n g…®n mangam, a tuavir God ian akurazim.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Rom 15:25; 2 Korin 8:4; 1 Tesalonika 1:3; 2 Timoti 1:18; Hibru 10:32-34\x*God a gumazir kuram puvat…®, a ingangarir aghuir ia amizibagh fo, ia God gifongezir arazimra God…®n gumazamizibar akagha men akurvasi, egha ia kamagh…®n amuav…®ra iti. Egh a bizir kaba bak…®n…®ghnighan kogham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Kolosi 2:2; Hibru 3:6; 3:14\x*E kamagh…®n bar ifonge, ia bizir aghuir ia fogha iniamibav zuam ik…®, kamagh…®n ia God gifongezir arazim…®n g…®n zui mogh…®n, ia bar mogh…®ra tuivigh gavgavighv…®ra ik…®, mang…®t…® ik…®r…®m…®rir kam g…®vagham.  
\v 12 Ia am…®rvaghan mark…®. Ia gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia egha zuam…®ram am…®rvazir puvat…®zibar m…®n ik…®. Egh bizir God fom…®ra uan boribar an…®ngasa akam ak…®riziba, ia da iniam. 
\s1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Jenesis 22:16-17\x*God fom…®ra akar d…®k…®r…®zim Abraham dan…®ngasa, a fo, gumazitam ekevegha a gafirazir puvat…®, egha a uab…® uan ziam d…®bora ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Jenesis 22:16-17\x*Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, k…® deragh n…® damuva, egh n…®n ovavir boribar amight…® me bar av…®rasemegham.‚Äù  
\v 15 Abraham a m…®zua zuam…®ram am…®rvazir puvat…®, ez…® God, g…®n bizir an akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n m…®rara Abraham dan…®ngasa m…®kemeziba, a gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:10-11\x*Gumazim gavgavim uan akam dan…®ng…®s…®, a gumazir a gafirazim…®n ziam d…®bora ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra. A kamagh…®n damight…®, gumazitam anedueghan kogham.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Rom 11:29; Hibru 11:9\x*God fom…®ra, gumazamiziba uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim me gan…®ngiz…®, me fo, me g…®n an akam ak…®rizir biziba iniam. Dughiar kam a deraghv…®ra kamagh…®n men akaghasa ifongegha ghaze, n…®ghn…®zir kam uam an otevk…®nighan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gavgavim uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim gan…®ga uan ziam d…®bora ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt D…®boboniba 23:19; 1 Samuel 15:29\x*Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n akar pumuning iti, kar God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim, ko God…®n arazir uan ziam d…®borim, aning otevk…®nighan kogham. God uab…® ifarir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e gumazamizir ara ghua God…®n borogh…®n mongeziba, e God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh e uan naviba gavgavim dar an…®ng, egh bizir aghuir e fogha iniamiba m…®zuamv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 6:19 \xt Ofa Gami 16:2-3; 16:12; 16:15; Hibru 9:7\x*Egha e bizir aghuir e fogha iniamiba bagha m…®zuair arazir kam, a en akuragha en ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n suiragha gavgavim e gan…®di, mati angka kurim…®n suiraz…® a gavgavigha danganir vam…®ran iti. E Iesus m…®zuaima, an aven ghua inir ekiar me God…®n D…®penim…®n gurazim…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n oto.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 6:20 \xt Ofa Gami 16:2-3; 16:12-15; Onger Akaba 110:4; Hibru 3:1; 5:6; 5:10; 7:17; 8:1; 9:24\x*Iesusra e bagha faraghav…®ra aven ghugha Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n oto. Egha a Melkisedegh…®n m…®n Ofa Gamir Gumazim…®n oto, egh a zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.\f + \fr 6:20 \ft Azeniba bar aruer vam…®ran dughiar vam…®ran Israelian ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ingangarir ekiar mam iti. An as…®zibar ghuzim inigh, egh arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® God…®n Purirpenim…®n Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n aven mangam. Danganir kam, God uab…® an aven iti. N…® Ofa Gamir Ak…®nafarim sapta 16, ko Hibrun Ak…®nafarim 9:1-7…®n gan. E fo, dat…®r…®gh…®n Iesus guiz…®n Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim…®n oto. Egha God…®n D…®penir an Nguibam…®n itim…®n a gumazamizibar arazir kuraba a g…®vasa ingangarim gami. N…® Hibru 4:14 ko 8:2…®n gan.\f* 
\c 7  
\s1 Melkisedek a ziar bar ekiam iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1-2 \xt Jenesis 14:17-20\x*Ia fo, Melkisedegh…®n kam, a Salem…®n nguibam…®n atrivim, egha a God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n ofa gamir gumazim. Ez…® dughiar mam Abraham atrivir 4pla m…®sogha me ab…®ni. Egha a uamategha izima, Melkisedek tuavim…®n a batogha a bagha God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God bizir aghuiba a bagh dar amuam.  
\v 2 Ez…® Abraham bizir a m…®dorozim…®n iniziba, a bar a da tuiraz…®, da 10plan pozibar otifi, ez…® a pozir mam isa Melkisedek gan…®ngi. (Ia n…®ghn…®gh, Melkisedegh…®n ziam…®n m…®ngarim a kamak…®n, Arazir Aghuibar Atrivim. Egha a uaghan Salem…®n atrivim, ez…® an ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Navir Am…®rizim…®n Atrivim.)  
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Onger Akaba 110:4\x*Ez…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven, me Melkisedegh…®n ameboghfeziabar ziaba osirizir puvat…®, egha an ovavitam…®n ziam osirizir puvat…®. Egha uaghan amebam a batezir dughiam ko an ovever dughiam me da osirizir puvat…®. A God…®n Otarim…®n m…®n ikia Ofa Gamir Gumazim…®n ikia mamagh…®ra iti.\f + \fr 7:3 \ft Melkisedek ameboghfeziaba puvat…®zir akam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n an ameboghfeziabar m…®g…®r…®g…®atam itir puvat…®. Ez…® an amebam a batezir dughiam ko an aremezir dughiam, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven m…®g…®r…®g…®atam itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir Hibrun Ak…®nafarim osirizim ghaze, Iesus ofa gamir gumazim…®n ikia zurara mamagh…®ra iti, ez…® Melkisedek purama an ababanim gami.\f* 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4 \xt Jenesis 14:20\x*Ia Melkisedegh…®n kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, a ziar bar ekiam iti! En inazir afeziar faragha zuim Abraham bizir a m…®dorozim…®n iniziba, a bar a da tuiraz…®, da 10plan pozibar otifi, ez…® a pozir mam isa Melkisedek gan…®ngi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt D…®boboniba 18:21\x*E fo, Livain ovaviba me God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar otifi. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, Israelian gumaziba, me uan biziba 10plan pozibar da tuiraght…®, Livain gumaziba me da pozitam iniam. Livaiba me uaghan Israelian marasi. Egha me uaghan Abraham…®n ovaviba. Ez…® Israelia uan biziba tuiragha maba isa uan marazigh an…®ngiz…® me da ini.  
\v 6 Melkisedek a Livain adarazir ovavim…®n otozir puvat…®. Ez…® Abraham uan biziba tuiraz…®, da 10plan pozibar otoz…®, Melkisedek a da pozir mam ini. Egha Melkisedek, bagha God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God bizir aghuiba a bagh dar amuam. Gumazir kam Abraham, a God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim ini.  
\v 7 E kamagh…®n fo, gumazim God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God bizir aghuiba gumazir igharazim damuam, a gumazir bar ekiam. Ez…® bizir aghuiba iniamin gumazim, an an apengan iti.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt Hibru 5:6; 6:20\x*Ez…® Livaiba me Israelian 10plan pozibar ar…®zir bizibar akuar maba isi, kar gumazir ovengamiba. Ez…® Melkisedekra, gumazir Abraham…®n bizir akuaba inizim, God…®n Ak…®nafarim ghaze, an ovever akatam itir puvat…®, a ik…®v…®ra ikiam.  
\v 9 E kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Livai uab…®, gumazir Israelian 10plan pozibar ar…®ghizir bizir akuaba inizim, a uaghan Abraham…®n ovavim…®n ikia, egha a tuavir kam…®n uan bizir akuaba isa Melkisedek gan…®ngi.  
\v 10 Guizbang…®ra, Livai t…®ghar otivamin dughiam…®n, a uan ovavim Abraham…®n m…®karzim…®n aven iti. Ez…® Melkisedek tuavim…®n Abraham batoz…® Abraham bizir kaba isa Melkisedek gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®ra e m…®k…®m suam, Livai uaghan uan biziba isa Melkisedek gan…®ngi. 
\s1 Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanir igiam, a fom…®ra itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazibagh afira 
\p  
\v 11 Fom…®ra Israelian gumazamiziba, Moses Osirizir Araziba ini, ez…® arazir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, Livain gumaziba God…®n ofa gamir ingangarim damu. Eght…® Livain gumazibar ofa gamir ingangarim, a gumazamizibar amut…® me bar deraghv…®ra ik…®t…®, manmaghsua God ghaze, ofa gamir gumazir igharazim g…®n otivam? A Melkisedegh…®n m…®n ik…®va, Aron…®n m…®n ikian kogham.  
\v 12 Eght…® God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar araziba iragh igharagh otivt…®ma, eght…® Moses Osirizir Araziba uaghan iragh igharagh otivam.  
\v 13 Ez…® en Ekiam, gumazir God…®n Ak…®nafarim gun m…®kemezim, an anabar igharazim…®n gumazim. Ez…® an anabam…®n adarazir tav dughiatam…®n God…®n ofa gamir ingangarim gamizir puvat…®.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Jenesis 49:10; Aisaia 11:1; Matyu 2:6; Akar Mogomem 5:5\x*Ez…® e bar fo, en Ekiam a Judan anabam…®n adarazir aven oto. Ez…® Moses ofa gamir gumazibar ingangarim m…®g…®a, anabar kam…®n adaraziv kemezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir igharazim otoz…® e an gari, a Melkisedegh…®n m…®raram oto. Egh e kamagh…®n deraghv…®ra fogham, a Livain ofa gamir gumaziba bar me gafira.  
\v 16 Gumazir kam ofa gamir gumazim…®n oto, me nguazir kam…®n arazibar g…®n ghua an anabam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ingangarir kam a gan…®ngizir pu. Puvat…®. An ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n gavgavim zurara ik…®t…® bizitam a gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. Gavgavir kam a gamiz…®ma a ofa gamir gumazim…®n oto.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Onger Akaba 110:4; Hibru 5:6\x*E fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúN…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\q2 N…® Melkisedegh…®n m…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
