\p  
\v 18-19 \x - \xo 7:18-19 \xt Rom 8:3; Galesia 2:16; 4:9; Efesus 2:18; Hibru 9:9\x*Kamagh…®n e fo, arazir ghurir kam, gavgaviba puvat…®gha egha a deragha en akurvazir puvat…®. Egha a bizitam gamima a derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God aneg…®fa. Egha God dat…®r…®gh…®n tuavir bar aghuir mam kui. Tuavir kamra kara, e bizir aghuir e fogha iniamiba bagha m…®zuai. Ez…® tuavir kam Moses Osirizir Arazibagh afira. E tuavir kam…®n mang…® God…®n borogh…®ra mangam. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® uaghan, dughiar God gumazir kam am…®sevez…® an ofa gamir gumazim…®n otozim, a pura anem…®sevezir puvat…®. A uab…® uan ziam d…®bora ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra, egha anem…®sefe. Ez…® me ofa gamir gumazir igharaziba am…®s…®vasa, gumazitam uan akam gavgavim gan…®ga God…®n ziam d…®borozir puvat…®.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 7:21 \xt Onger Akaba 110:4; Hibru 5:6\x*God uab…® guizbang…®ra m…®kemez…®, tuavir kam…®n Iesus ofa gamir gumazim…®n oto. God kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam bar guizbang…®ra m…®kemegha 
\q2 akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, 
\q1 ‚ÄòN…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n ik…® 
\q2 mamagh…®ra ikiam,‚Äô 
\q3 egh uan n…®ghn…®zim giraghan kogham.‚Äù 
\b  
\m  
\v 22 \x - \xo 7:22 \xt Hibru 8:6; 12:24\x*God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam kamagh…®n en akaz…® e fo, Iesus Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam deragh an gan…®va a damight…®, a guizbang…®ram otogham. E fo, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam a bar deragha, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ghurim gafira. 
\p  
\v 23 Fom…®ra, gumazir av…®rim God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar otifi. Egha me ariaghira, egha uan ingangarim gamir puvat…®. Bizir kam bagha, gumazir av…®riba ofa gamir gumazibar otifi.  
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra ikiav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n a God…®n ofa gamir ingangarim gamua mamagh…®ra ikiav…®ra iti. Eght…® tav an m…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n otoghan kogham.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 7:25 \xt Rom 8:34; 1 Timoti 2:5; Hibru 9:24; 1 Jon 2:1\x*An angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra ikia egha gumazamiziba bagha God…®n azangs…®si. An ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n a me inigha God…®n borogh…®ra zui. Kamagh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n ko zurara, a men akurvagham. 
