\v 8 \x - \xo 8:8-12 \xt Jeremaia 31:31-34\x*Egha God uan gumazamizibar arazir kuraba aghurigha kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® ian Ekiam, 
