\q1  
\v 11 \x - \xo 8:11 \xt Aisaia 54:13; Jon 6:45; 1 Jon 2:27\x*Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba vaghvagh uan namakaba ko uan adarazir sure damuan kogh suam, 
