\v 16 Gumazim n…®ghn…®gh suam, a g…®n aremegham, egh suam gumazir manam an biziba iniam, egh an ak…®nafarim osirigham. Kar mati an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim. Eght…® borim Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mang…®, egh afeziam a ginabazir biziba iniam. Eght…® gumaziba deragh fogh suam, afeziam aremegha g…®fa, egh me biziba bar an borim…®n tegham.  
