\v 18 \x - \xo 9:18 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:6\x*Ez…® kamagh…®ra, me as…®zim m…®soghez…® an aremez…®, me an ghuzim inge, egha tuavir kamra Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir faragha ikezim gamiz…®ma, a gavgafi.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 9:19 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:3-8; Ofa Gami 14:4-7; 16:14-15\x*\x - \xo 9:19-20 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:6-8\x*Dughiar kam…®n, Moses faragha God…®n Akar Gavgaviba, bar dar gun gumazamizibav keme. Akar kaba, da Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven iti. Egha a g…®n bulmakaun apuribar ghuzim ko memebar ghuzim inigha d…®pam sara da vere. Egha a, isop…®n temer agharir me benir aghevim…®n ikezim, benir kam me sipsip…®n ar…®zibar an ingari, Moses a inigha ghuzim gat…®. Egha an anesigha temer agharir kam…®n ghuzir muziarim inigha Akar Gavgavim…®n itir Ak…®nafarim ko gumazamiziba bar me gis…®n a kavamadi.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 9:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:8; Matyu 26:28\x*Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar ghuzir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gavgavim a dan…®ngamim. God Akar Gavgavim ia gan…®ga ghaze, ia Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 21 \x - \xo 9:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 29:12; 29:36; Ofa Gami 8:15; 8:19\x*Kamagh…®ra Moses ghuzir muziarim inigha God…®n Purirpenim ko God…®n ziam fer bizibagh is…®n a kavamadi.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Ofa Gami 17:11; Efesus 1:7\x*Guizbang…®ra, e ti kamagh m…®k…®m suam, Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, ghuzimra bizibar amight…®, da God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegham. Eght…® me bizitam m…®suegh an ghuzim inigh a ingeghan koght…®, God gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham. 
