\v 18 E kamagh…®n ganigha fo, God arazir kuraba g…®n amadaz…®, kamagh…®n uam arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin ofaba, da ua ingangariba puvat…®. 
\s1 E guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®va egh God…®n borogh…®ra mangam 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 10:19 \xt Rom 5:2; Efesus 2:18; 3:12; Hibru 4:16; 9:8\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nan adarasi, Iesus…®n ghuzim en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagha g…®fa. Egh tuavir kam…®n e Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n aven mang…® egh atiatingan kogham.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 10:20 \xt Matyu 27:51; Jon 10:9; 14:6; Hibru 9:3; 9:8\x*Iesus aremegha ua angam…®ra iti, an e bagha tuavir igiar kam kui, tuavir ikia mamagh…®ra itim. A tuavir kam…®n inir ekiar kam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n ghua danganir kam…®n aven ghu, inir kam a danganir kam…®n tiar akam…®n m…®n guraghav iti. Ez…® inir kam, a mati an m…®karzim…®n ovevemra. Eght…® e tuavir kam…®n danganir kam…®n aven mangam.\f + \fr 10:20 \ft Bar Anogoroghezir Danganir kam, kar God uab…® itir danganim. Fom…®ra ofa gamir gumazibar dapanimra danganir kam…®n an an aven zui. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Iesus amizir ingangarim…®n, e bar mogh…®ra God…®n borogh…®n mangam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Iesus…®n m…®karzim ab…®ghiz…® a ter ighuvim…®n ovengez…®, inir ekiar Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n itiar akam itim tong…®ra bighiaghir…®gha akuar pumuning oto. N…® Mak 15:38…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 10:21 \xt Hibru 4:14\x*E Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Dapanim iti, ez…® a God…®n gumazamiziba bar men gara me gatifa.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Ofa Gami 8:30; Esekiel 36:25; Efesus 3:12; 5:26; Hibru 9:14; Jems 1:6; 1 Jon 3:21\x*A uan ghuzim isa en navir averiaba dav k…®niz…® an e ak…®riz…®, e kamagh…®n fo, e arazir kuraba puvat…®gha God…®n damazim…®n bar zue. Egha a d…®par bar d…®k…®riam…®n en m…®karziba rue. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ifavarir arazir en navir averiabar itiba, e bar ada ategh…®va, okam n…®ghn…®ghan kogh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®, egh an borogh…®n mangam.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:24; 2 Tesalonika 3:3; Hibru 4:14; 11:11\x*E fo, bizir God ingarasa akam ak…®riziba, a bar guizbang…®ra dar ingaram. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar gun m…®g…®a ghaze, bizir aghuir e fogha iniamiba bagha m…®zua iti. Egh e uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n suiragh bar gavgavigham.  
\v 24 E vaghvagh God…®n gumazamizir igharazibagh n…®ghn…®gh…®va, me damut…® men naviba d…®kavt…®, me igharaz darazigh ifuegh, arazir aghuibar me damuam.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 10:25 \xt Rom 13:11; Filipai 4:5; Hibru 3:13; 2 Pita 3:9-11; 3:14\x*Ez…® e God…®n gumazamiziba, e uari akuvir arazim atagh…®raghan kogham, mati gumazamizir maba ami mok…®n. Kamagh…®n mark…®. E fo, Dughiar Ekiam Gumazamiziba Tuis…®ghamim, a rogh…®ra izi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e vaghvagh pamtem ingar…®va, igharaz darazir akurvagh egh gavgavim me dan…®ngam. 
\s1 E God…®n Otarim ak…®rim ragh a gasan kogham 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 10:26 \xt D…®boboniba 15:30; Hibru 6:4-8; 2 Pita 2:20-21\x*Ia oragh. E guiz…®n akam g…®fogh a inigh, egh g…®n m…®k…®m suam, mark…®, egh uan ifongiabar g…®n mang…® arazir kurabar amuv…®ra ikiam, eght…® kamagh…®n ua ofa damuamin tuavir igharaziba puvat…®gham.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 10:27 \xt Aisaia 26:11; Hibru 12:29\x*Ez…® bizir e damuamin mam kamagh…®n iti: E atiatir kuram damuva God…®n Kotiam…®n Dughiam ko, avir bar puv…®ra isim m…®zuamam. Avir kam God…®n apanibar isi me gas…®ghas…®gham.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 10:28 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:6; 19:15; Jon 8:17; 2 Korin 13:1\x*E fo, gumazitam Moses Osirizir Arazitam baraghan aghuagham, eght…® gumazir pumuning o pumuning ko m…®kezim ganigh egh an gun m…®kemegham, eght…® me an apangkuvan mark…®, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 10:29 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:8; 1 Korin 11:29; Efesus 4:30; Hibru 12:25\x*Ia manmagh…®n gumazir ak…®rim ragha God…®n Otarim gasarazim g…®n…®ghn…®si? Gumazir kam a bar os…®mt…®zir ekiam iniam. Egh an ivezir kuram, gumazir Moses Osirizir Araziba batoghezim…®n ivezir kuram, bar a gafiragham. Krais…®n ghuzim Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam gamima a gavgafi. Ez…® ghuzir kam gumazir kam gamiz…®ma a zuegha God…®n gumazim…®n oto. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir kam a Krais…®n ghuzim m…®g…®a ghaze, a pura bizim. Egha a, God…®n Duar apangkuvim en itim, an tiragha akaba a gasi.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 10:30 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:35-36; Onger Akaba 50:4; 135:14; Rom 12:19\x*Ez…® e fo, God kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúArazir kuraba ikarvaghamin ingangarim, ka nan bizim. K…® uab…® men arazir kuraba ikarvagh egh ivezir kuraba me dan…®ngam.‚Äù Egha ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam uab…® uan gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham.‚Äù  
\v 31 \x - \xo 10:31 \xt Luk 12:5\x*Kamagh…®n, God…®n ikia mamagh…®ra itim, a tav…®n suiragh ivezir kuram a dan…®ngam, eght…® gumazir kam guizbang…®ram atiatingam. 
\s1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n suiragh gavgavigham 
\p  
\v 32 \x - \xo 10:32 \xt Galesia 3:4; Filipai 1:29-30; Kolosi 2:1; Hibru 6:4\x*Ia dughiar faragha ghuzim uam a g…®n…®ghn…®gh, dughiar ia Akar Aghuim…®n angazangarim inigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n an itim. Dughiar kam…®n me os…®mt…®zir ekiaba ia gar…®zima, ez…® ia m…®zazir av…®riba ini. Egha ia tuivigha gavgaviz…® os…®mt…®zir kaba ia d…®kab…®razir puvat…®.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 10:33 \xt 1 Korin 4:9; Filipai 1:7; 4:14; 1 Tesalonika 2:14\x*Ez…® dughiar maba me gumazamizibar damazibar ia afima ia tuivav iti, ez…® me d…®bovir akabar ia m…®g…®a egha paza ia gami. Egha dughiar mabar os…®mt…®zir kamagh gariba aterir gumaziba, ia men puegha me ko iti.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 10:34 \xt Matyu 6:20; 19:21; 19:29; Luk 12:38; Aposel 5:41; Filipai 1:7; Jems 1:2\x*Egha dughiar me ian marazi isa kalabus gat…®zim, ia men kuarkuva derav…®ra me gami. Ez…® dughiar me ian biziba suiragha inigha ghuziba, pura men gara bar akuegha iti. Ia kamagh…®n guizbang…®ra fo, ian bizir ia g…®n iniamiba God…®n Nguibam…®n ia m…®zua ikia mamagh…®ra iti. 
