\v 35 \x - \xo 10:35 \xt Matyu 5:12; 10:32\x*Kamagh…®n, ia arazir aghuir ia faragha amizibagh n…®ghnigh, uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam deragh an suiragh, egh bizir k…®nim…®n m…®n puram a makunan mark…®. Egh ia kamagh…®n damuva ivezir aghuir ekiam iniam.  
\v 36 \x - \xo 10:36 \xt Luk 21:19; Galesia 6:9; Kolosi 3:24; Hibru 9:15; 12:1\x*Ia God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…®va, egh bizir aghuir a fom…®ra ia dan…®ngasa akam ak…®riziba, ia da inis…®, tuivigh gavgavigh ik…®.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 10:37 \xt 2 Pita 3:9\x*\x - \xo 10:37-38 \xt Habakuk 2:3-4\x*Guizbang…®ra, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
