\v 4 \x - \xo 11:4 \xt Jenesis 4:3-10; Hibru 12:24; 1 Jon 3:12\x*Abel n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, egha bizir kam bagha God…®n ofa gami. An ofa God…®n damazim bar deragha, Kein…®n ofa gafira. Abel n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti, ez…® bizir kam bagha God Abel…®n bizir aghuir an a gan…®dim bagha ifonge. Ez…® bizir kam kamagh…®n en aka, God a m…®g…®a ghaze, a gumazir aghuim. Abel an aremegha g…®fa. Ez…® an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, dat…®r…®gh…®n an akam…®n gun e m…®g…®av…®ra iti. 
