\v 5 \x - \xo 11:5 \xt Jenesis 5:21-24\x*Ez…® Enok uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti. Ez…® bizir kam bagha God a inigha uan Nguibam…®n ghuavanaboz…® an aremezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba a buria, an apizir Puvat…®, God a inigha ghuavanabo. God…®n Ak…®nafarim ghaze, God t…®ghar Enok iniamin dughiam…®n, an araziba bar God…®n damazim…®n deraz…® an a bagha bar akonge.  
\v 6 Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itir puvat…®zim, a God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mangan koght…® an a bagh bar akongeghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, gumazir God…®n borogh…®ra mangasava amim, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n ik…®, God a iti. Egh a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n ik…®, God derav…®ra gumazamizir a buribagh ami. 
