\v 7 \x - \xo 11:7 \xt Jenesis 6:13-22; 7:1; Rom 3:22; 4:13; 1 Pita 3:20\x*Ez…® Noa uaghan kamagh…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti. Ez…® God bizir g…®n otivamibar gun a m…®keme. Kar bizir Noa t…®ghar ganamiba. Egha a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n akam…®n ikia, egha bizir kam bagha a kurir mam…®n ingari. Egha uan amuiroghboriba ko, me kurim…®n aven ghuez…®, bizitam me gas…®ghas…®zir puvat…®z…®, me derav…®ra iti. Ez…® Noan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, a nguazim…®n itir gumazamizir igharaziba bar, men arazir kuraba da aghurigha azenim gat…®. Noa n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itima, God bizir kam…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, a nan damazim…®n bar gumazir aghuim. Ez…® God bar gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, a bar kamagh…®ra me gami. 
