\v 8 \x - \xo 11:8 \xt Jenesis 12:1-5; Aposel 7:2-4\x*Ez…® uaghan Abraham n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti. Egha bizir kam bagha God an diazir dughiam…®n, Abraham God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua, egha uan nguibam ataki. Egha a nguibar God a dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizim…®n ghu, kar guiz…®n an nguibamra. Ez…® Abraham fozir puvat…®, a managh mangam. Egha a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia egha a zui.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 11:9 \xt Jenesis 12:8; 13:3; 13:18; 18:1; 18:9; 26:3; 35:12; 35:27; Hibru 6:17\x*A n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia ghua nguazir kam…®n apera, nguazir God fom…®ra a dan…®ngasa akam ak…®rizim. Egha a nguazir kam gaperagha mati nguibar igharazim…®n gumazim. A Purirpenim gaperaghav iti, mogh…®n Aisak ko Jekop uaghan uan purirpenibagh apiaghav iti, gumazir kamning God nguazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha egha uaghan akar kam aning bagha anek…®ri.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 11:10 \xt Hibru 3:4; 13:14; Akar Mogomem 21:2; 21:10\x*Abraham zurara n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia nguibar ekiar gavgavigha itir kam…®n ganasa m…®zua iti. Nguibar ekiar kam, God uab…®ra tuavir an ingaramibagh n…®ghnigha, egha uab…® an ingari.\f + \fr 11:10 \ft Nguibar ekiar kam Jerusalem, a God…®n Nguibam…®n iti. N…® Hibru 12:2…®n gan egh fogh.\f* 
