\v 11 \x - \xo 11:11 \xt Jenesis 17:19; 18:11-14; 21:2; Rom 4:21; Hibru 10:23\x*Ez…® Sara uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n iti. A guizbang…®n bar ghurigha boritam batan kogham. Egha a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Egha borim batamin gavgavim ini. Sara kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúGod na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® boritam batam,‚Äô egha akam k…®ri. K…® fo, God guizbang…®ra m…®keme.‚Äù  
\v 12 \x - \xo 11:12 \xt Jenesis 15:5; 22:17; 32:12; God…®n Araziba 10:22; Rom 4:18-19\x*Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam Abraham a ghurigha egha aremeghasava ami, egha an ovavir borir av…®ribar afeziam…®n oto. Ez…® an ovaviba otiva bar av…®raseme, mati overiam…®n m…®koveziba, o ongarim…®n dadarim…®n gigiba. Gumazitam da meng…®va avegham. 
