\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 11:20 \xt Jenesis 27:27-29; 27:39-40\x*Kamagh…®ra Aisak n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia egha Jekop ko Iso g…®n…®ghn…®gha akam ak…®ra ghaze, God g…®n izamin dughiabar, derav…®ra gua damuam. 
