\v 21 Ez…® kamagh…®ra Jekop a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, egha an aremeghasava amir dughiam…®n, a Josep…®n otarimning m…®g…®a ghaze, God derav…®ra gua damu. Egha a uan fidizir zurara suiagha aruim gis…®n aviragha God…®n ziam fe. 
