\v 22 \x - \xo 11:22 \xt Jenesis 50:24-25; Ua Me Ini 13:19\x*Ez…® kamagh…®ra Josep n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God ikia, egha dughiar an ovengamim…®n a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelia g…®n kantri Isip ategh mangam. Egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, me manmagh…®n an kuam damuam. 
