\v 23 \x - \xo 11:23 \xt Ua Me Ini 1:22; 2:2; Aposel 7:20\x*Ez…® Moses…®n afeziam ko amebam aning n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, egha dughiar amebam Moses batezim…®n, aning an garima a borir bar dirim. Aning atrivim…®n akam batoghan atiatingizir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning iak…®nir 3plan a modo. 
