\v 28-29 \x - \xo 12:28-29 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:24; 9:3; Onger Akaba 50:3; Aisaia 33:14; Hibru 10:27\x*Bizibagh Ativamin Danganir e inizir kam, an akongan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e danganir kam bagh a m…®nabagham. E fo, en God mati avir puv…®ra bizibagh as…®ghas…®zim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e an atiating…®va an apengan ik…®, egh a m…®nab…®va a uab…® ifongezir arazim…®n g…®n mang…® an ziam fam. 
