\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Jon 13:34; 1 Tesalonika 4:9; 1 Pita 1:22; 2 Pita 1:7; 1 Jon 3:11; 4:7; 4:20\x*Ia Krais…®n adarasi, ia vaghvagh uarigh ifongegh mamagh…®ra ik…®, mati ia uan adarazigh ifongez…® mok…®n.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Jenesis 18:1-8; 19:1-3; Matyu 25:35; Rom 12:13; 1 Timoti 3:2; 1 Pita 4:9\x*Nguibar igharazibar gumaziba ian bighan izamin dughiabar, ia me inigh uan d…®penibar mang…®s…® ok…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Ia fo, fom…®ra gumazamizir maba ghaze, me gumazir k…®niba isa uan d…®penibar ghua egha men gari. Ez…® gumazir me inigha izir kaba, me enselba. Me ghaze, me guiz…®n gumazibar gari, ez…® puvat…®, me enselbara gari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt Matyu 25:36; Rom 12:15; 1 Korin 12:26; Kolosi 4:18; Hibru 10:34; 1 Pita 3:8\x*Ia God…®n gumazamizir kalabus…®n itibagh n…®ghn…®gh, mati ia me ko kalabus…®n iti. Egh ia uaghan gumazir men apaniba paza me gamizibagh n…®ghn…®gh. Ia fo, ia nguazir kam…®n ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® apaniba uaghan ti arazir kamra ia damuam. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt 1 Korin 6:9; Galesia 5:19-21; Efesus 5:5; Kolosi 3:5-6; Akar Mogomem 22:15\x*Ia bar kamagh…®n fogh, gumazim ko amizim uaning…®n ikia poroghamimning…®n otozir arazim, a bizir bar aghuim, egha God…®n damazim…®n dera. Ez…® ia poroghamiba bar derav…®ra uan arazibar gan. Eght…® God g…®n ivezir kuram is…®, gumazamizir uari bak…®ava akuiba ko afiar arazibagh amir gumazamizibar an…®ngam. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 13:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:6-8; Josua 1:5; Matyu 6:25; 6:34; Filipai 4:11-12; 1 Timoti 6:8\x*Ia dag…®ar av…®riba ik…®s…® ifueghan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh, bizir ia itiba, da ian tughat…®zir puvat…®. Ia fo, God kamagh…®n e m…®kemegha g…®fa: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® ia ateght…® 
\q2 bizitam paza ia damuan kogham. 
\q3 Bar puvat…®. 
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, k…® ia ateghan kogham.‚Äù 
