\m  
\v 6 \x - \xo 13:6 \xt Onger Akaba 118:6\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e gavgavim uan navibar an…®ng egh m…®k…®m suam: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam nan Akurvazir Gumazim, 
\q2 na ko itima 
\q3 k…® atiatir puvat…®. 
\q1 K…® fo, 
\q2 gumazamiziba arazitam…®n na damighan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 E Iesus…®n g…®n mang…®s…® aghums…®ghan kogham 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 13:7 \xt 1 Korin 4:16; Hibru 6:12\x*Ia uan sios…®n gumazamizir dapanibagh n…®ghn…®gh, me fom…®ra God…®n akam…®n gun ia m…®keme. Ia men arazir aghuiba ko men ovevem g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Egh men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim, ia uaghan an g…®n mang…®.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 13:8 \xt Jon 8:58; Efesus 4:14; Hibru 1:12; Akar Mogomem 1:4\x*Krais Iesus…®n arazim, a fom…®ra kamagh…®ra ikia dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia, egh a g…®n zurara kamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 13:9 \xt Rom 14:17; Efesus 4:14; Kolosi 2:8; 2:16; 1 Timoti 4:3\x*Ia Akar Aghuim…®n m…®n zuir puvat…®zir akar igharaziba ateght…®, da ian n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ght…®, ia God…®n g…®n zuir tuavir aghuim atagh…®raghan mark…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e God…®n apangkuvim amamangat…®ght…® a gavgavim en navir averiabar an…®ngam. Dagheba apir arazim gavgavim en navir averiabar an…®ngan kogham. Arazir kam, gumazamizibar darorim…®n akurvazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt 1 Korin 9:13; 10:18\x*Ez…® e God…®n ofa gamir dakozir mam iti. Ez…® Judabar Purirpenim…®n aven ofa gamizir gumaziba, God men anogoroghez…®ma, me ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n daghebar aman kogham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 13:11 \xt Ua Me Ini 29:14; Ofa Gami 6:30; 16:27; D…®boboniba 19:3\x*Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, an as…®zibar ghuziba inigha Bar Anogoroghezir Danganir kam…®n aven ghugha, arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa ofa gami. Egha as…®zir kabar kuaba inigha gumazamiziba iti nagh…®n azenan ghua saghon da tuema, da isia m…®gh…®ri.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 13:12 \xt Matyu 21:39; Jon 19:17-18; Aposel 7:58\x*Kamagh…®ra, Iesus uaghan nguibar ekiam…®n azenan m…®zazim ini. A ghaze, a uan ghuzim…®n gumazamizibar amight…® me God…®n damazim…®n zuegh egh God…®n gumazamizibar otivigham, kamagh…®n an areme.\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, gumazamiziba God…®n ofa damuasa inigha izir as…®ziba, ofa gamir gumaziba da api. Me as…®zir gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, dughiar ekiabar ofa gamiba, me dar aman kogham. N…® Ofa Gami 6:24 ko 24:30 ko 16:27…®n gan. Dat…®r…®gh…®n, ofan dughiar ekiar kam, Iesus amizir ofan kam an danganim ini. N…® Hibru 9:7 ko 14…®n gan.\f* 
\v 13 \x - \xo 13:13 \xt Hibru 11:26; 12:2; 1 Pita 4:14\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e uaghan a bagh nguibam…®n azenan mang…®va, egh a inizir aghums…®zim e uaghan a iniam.\f + \fr 13:13 \ft Gumazir maba ti, Krais…®n g…®n zuir darazir amight…®, me Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir dagheba apir arazim…®n g…®n mangasa. (N…® ves 9…®n gan.) Ez…® gumazir Hibrun ak…®nafarim osirizim ghaze, Krais…®n g…®n zuir darasi, Judaba itir nguibabar ikian markiam. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, Moses Osirizir Araziba me damut…®, me God…®n damazim…®n zuegham. Puvat…®. Iesus…®n ingangarimrama me zuegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me a ko ik…®s…® aghums…®ghan kogh, anar…®ra g…®n mangam.\f* 
\v 14 \x - \xo 13:14 \xt Filipai 3:20; Hibru 11:10; 11:16; 12:22\x*E fo, nguazir kam…®n e zurara ikiamin nguibar ekiatam itir puvat…®. Egha e nguibar g…®n izamim bagha m…®zua iti.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 13:15 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 29:31; Onger Akaba 50:14; 50:23; 69:30-31; Hosea 14:2; 1 Pita 2:5\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n, e zurara ziar ekiam is…® ofan m…®n God dan…®ng mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® en akatoriba zurara an ziam f…® suam, a en Ekiam.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 13:16 \xt Rom 12:13; Filipai 4:18; Hibru 6:10\x*Egh ia arazir aghuibar gumazamizibar amu. Me bizitabar oteveght…®, ia men akurvaghs…® bizitaba me dan…®ng. Ofan kamagh…®n gariba, God bar dagh ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia arazir kabar amus…® ok…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. 
\s1 God e damut…® e derav…®ra ikiam 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 13:17 \xt Esekiel 3:17; 1 Tesalonika 5:12; 1 Timoti 5:17\x*Ian gumazir dapaniba ian akurvaghasa zurara ian gari. Egh me g…®n ingangarir me amizibar gun God ko m…®k…®mam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia men akaba baragh egh men apengan ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, me bar akuegh uan ingangarim damuam. Ia kamagh…®n damuan koght…®, me os…®mt…®zim sara ian ganam, eght…® bizir kam ian akuraghan kogham.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 13:18 \xt Aposel 23:1; 24:16; Rom 15:30; 2 Korin 1:12; Kolosi 4:3\x*Ia e bagh God ko m…®k…®mv…®ra ik…®. E kamagh…®n bar fo, e dughiabar zurara arazir aghuibara amuasa bar ifonge. E uan araziba bar derav…®ra da tuis…®gha arazir aghuibar g…®n ghua egha en navir averiaba os…®mt…®ziba God…®n damazim…®n puvat…®.  
\v 19 K…® m…®gh…®ra ia gakaghori, ia na bagh God ko m…®k…®m suam, a nan akuragh na amadaght…® k…® zuam…®ra ia bagh izam. 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 13:20 \xt Aisaia 55:3; Jeremaia 32:40; Esekiel 37:26; Sekaraia 9:11; Rom 15:33; 1 Korin 6:14; 1 Pita 2:25\x*K…® ia bagha God ko m…®gei, God…®n Navir Am…®rizim…®n M…®ngarim, a en Ekiam Iesus ovevem…®n a gamiz…® a ua d…®kafi. Iesus, Sipsipbar Garir Gumazir Gavgavim Itim, a uab…® ofan m…®n aremegha uan ghuzim…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, gavgavim a gan…®ngi, eght…® a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 13:21 \xt Galesia 1:5; Filipai 2:13; 2 Tesalonika 2:17; 1 Pita 5:10\x*Ez…® k…® ia bagha God…®n kam ko m…®g…®a kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, eght…® a ian akuragh gavgavim ia dan…®ngt…®, ia arazir aghuibar amu, egh an ifongiam…®n g…®n mangam. Eght…® Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n, an en navir averiabar aven ingart…®, e a ifongezir arazibar amuam. Egh e zurazurara ziar ekiam a dan…®ng mamagh…®ra ikiam. Bar guizbang…®ra. 
