\p  
\v 22 Nan adarasi, akar k…® ia bagha osirizir kam, a ruarazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia n…®m…®ra ik…®, egh akar k…® gavgavim ian navibar an…®ngasa osirizir kam, ia derav…®ram a baragh.  
\v 23 K…® kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa ifonge, me kalabus…®n en aveghbuam Timoti f…®riz…®, a ua kalabus…®n itir puvat…®. A zuam…®ra na bagh izegh…®va, ga uaghara mang…® ian ganam. 
\p  
\v 24 Ia uan gumazir dapaniba ko God…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®m suam, k…® ghaze, God deraghv…®ra me damu. Ez…® Kantri Italin itir Krais…®n adarazi uaghan ia bagha akam amaga ghaze, God deraghv…®ra ia damu. 
